<p>If you are interested in coaching high school lacrosse in the state of Indiana please contact Paul Borchelt at <a href="mailto:pborchelt@gmail.com">pborchelt@gmail.com</a>. 
 Coaching lacrosse is very similar to coaching other sports. If you are interested in coaching lacrosse the IHSLA can help train you as well as US Lacrosse. 
 
